<typeStatus id="FF353EAE1A1BFFA4FDE08034FDD19A64" box="[584,632,1843,1869]" pageId="26" pageNumber="177">type</typeStatus>
series was collected in mid-June in grassy steppes.Adults were observed flying among vegetation (Junnilainen &amp; Nupponen 2010: 9).
</paragraph>
